This directory contains various tools for Day Planner.
Some of them are only useful for development or debugging, while
others might be useful for other things too.

buildpot		Build the Day Planner POT file to ../po/dayplanner.pot

BuildLocale		Build a localization tree in ../locale/ with mo-files
			and a proper gettext directory structure

postat			View translation statistics

updatepo		Run buildpot and then msgmerge existing *.po files with
			the new pot-file

installer/		Contains the source code for the generic Day Planner
			installer

rpm/			Contains the specfiles for the Day Planner RPM
